        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Asimov', 3: 'You belong to the same team, so your connections are interconnected. It won\\'t be too hard for you to hack into Liv\\'s M.I.N.D., and 【kuroname】 will also help stabilize the Mind Beacon.', 4: '13'}"
